marketing: PENNZOIL^® PREMIUM OUTBOARD AND MULTI-PURPOSE TWO-CYCLE OIL contains only ashless components which prevent any lubricant related preignition and plug fouling. The ashless additives protect against piston and combustion chamber deposits, rust, and corrosion. It resists gel formulation due to water or other contamination. The special base stocks used resist piston and cylinder scuffing.
